ication with the artificial intelligence that controls the entire place, which has been quietly observing them until it could learn their language and intentions.					</p>					<p>						<strong>Next:</strong>						<a href="../2">							Veil of the Foundation: Part 3, Episode 2						</a>					</p>				</section><? require $_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] . "/includes/footer-global.php" ?>